---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import { localPath } from "../../lib/i18n";

const lang = "it";
---

<Layout
  title="Contatti | Keryx Design"
  description="Lavoriamo solo con chi è pronto. Candidati per un progetto e scopri se siamo il fit giusto."
  lang={lang}
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative min-h-[50vh] flex items-center bg-marble">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-16 lg:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-[64px] leading-[1.05] mb-6 text-foreground">
          Lavoriamo Solo con Chi &egrave; Pronto
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          Ecco perch&eacute; chiediamo una candidatura prima di iniziare.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Application Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-primary text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-6 text-primary-foreground">
          Perch&eacute; Candidatura?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-foreground/90 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Non prendiamo tutti i progetti che arrivano.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-primary-foreground/80 mb-8">
          Selezioniamo massimo 3 nuovi clienti al mese perch&eacute;:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 mb-10">
          {[
            "Ogni progetto riceve supervisione personale",
            "Non deleghiamo a junior o subappaltiamo",
            "La qualit\u00e0 non si scala, si protegge",
            "Preferiamo dire \u201Cno\u201D che consegnare lavoro mediocre",
          ].map((reason) => (
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold flex-shrink-0 mt-1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
              <span class="text-lg text-primary-foreground/90">{reason}</span>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
        <div class="border-l-4 border-gold pl-6">
          <p class="text-xl text-primary-foreground mb-3 leading-relaxed">
            La candidatura ci aiuta a capire se c&rsquo;&egrave; fit.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-primary-foreground/80 leading-relaxed">
            Se non c&rsquo;&egrave;, te lo diciamo subito. Zero tempo perso.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How It Works Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-background">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-12 text-foreground text-center">
          Come Funziona
        </h2>

        <!-- Vertical Timeline -->
        <div class="relative pl-12 md:pl-16">
          <!-- Vertical gold line -->
          <div class="absolute left-[18px] md:left-[22px] top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-gold/40"></div>

          {[
            "Compila il form di candidatura (5 minuti)",
            "Chiamata strategica di 30 minuti (se c\u2019\u00e8 potenziale fit)",
            "Ricevi proposta personalizzata con timeline e investimento",
            "Decidi se procedere",
          ].map((step, index) => (
            <div class="relative mb-10 last:mb-0">
              <!-- Gold circle with number -->
              <div class="absolute -left-12 md:-left-16 top-0 w-10 h-10 md:w-11 md:h-11 rounded-full bg-gold flex items-center justify-center shadow-md">
                <span class="text-primary font-bold text-lg">{index + 1}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="bg-card border border-border rounded-lg p-6 shadow-card">
                <p class="text-lg text-foreground leading-relaxed">{step}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>

        <p class="text-center text-lg text-muted-foreground mt-12 leading-relaxed">
          Semplice. Trasparente. Rispettoso del tuo tempo.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary/5 via-background to-gold/5">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <a
          href={localPath("/questionario", lang)}
          class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-gold hover:bg-gold-dark text-primary font-bold px-10 py-5 text-lg rounded-lg shadow-xl transition-colors group"
        >
          CANDIDATI PER UN PROGETTO
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
        </a>

        <div class="mt-10">
          <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-3">Hai una Domanda Veloce?</p>
          <a
            href="mailto:info@keryxdesign.com"
            class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-primary hover:text-primary/80 transition-colors font-medium text-lg"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"/><path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"/></svg>
            info@keryxdesign.com
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Newsletter Section -->
  <section class="py-20 lg:py-32 bg-primary">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl mb-6 text-primary-foreground">
          Non Sei Pronto per un Progetto?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl text-primary-foreground/90 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
          Inizia con il nostro corso email gratuito.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-primary-foreground/80 mb-2 leading-relaxed">
          10 lezioni sul Direct Response Design.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-primary-foreground/70 mb-10">
          Zero obblighi. Cancellati quando vuoi.
        </p>

        <!-- ConvertKit Embed -->
        <div data-uid="f28b14d401"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <script async data-uid="f28b14d401" src="https://keryxdesign.ck.page/f28b14d401/index.js"></script>
</Layout>
